author: Wayne Cole
title: Asia shares off to cautious start, U.S. crude slides
description: Caution gripped Asian share markets on Monday on expectations a busy week of corporate earnings reports and economic data will drive home the damage done by the global virus lockdown, while U.S. crude prices took an early spill.
content:
